---- Highlight new comments on an HN thread since your last checkpoint.

This is a GreaseMonkey js script whose content is injected into HN comments threads only.

-- Features
Adds the following buttons below the 'add comment' zone:

- 'Track comments': each comment is md5 hashed and looked up in the GreaseMonkey KV store of this thread. If not
found, it is marked as new (highlighted in the page) and added to the persistence.

- 'Clear current': clears the persistence of the current thread.

- 'Clear all': clears the persistence of all threads.

-- Install
Rename to hncomments.user.js. 
Open with Firefox / Chrome.

-- Privacy
Everything is stored locally.
